@startuml class_diagram_5
!include _thesis_style.puml
hide empty members
skinparam dpi 200
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam nodesep 18
skinparam ranksep 40

' Bagian 5/5: modul administrasi registri instansi (Option C).
' Super admin mengelola tabel agencies (system of record), lalu memuat ulang
' cache server inferensi melalui endpoint /reload-agencies.

package "features.admin" <<Modul Administrasi>> {
    class AgencyRegistryScreen <<ConsumerWidget>> {
        +build(context, ref) : Widget
        -openEditor(a: Agency?) : Future<void>
        -reload() : Future<void>
    }
    class AgencyRegistryRepository {
        -client: SupabaseClient
        -crmApiUrl: String
        +fetchAll() : Future<List<Agency>>
        +save(a: Agency) : Future<void>
        +setActive(id, isActive) : Future<void>
        +delete(id) : Future<void>
        +reloadInferenceServer() : Future<AgencyReloadResult>
    }
    class Agency <<model>> {
        +id: String
        +name: String
        +category: IssueCategory
        +latitude: double?
        +longitude: double?
        +isActive: bool
        +{static} fromMap(map) : Agency
        +toMap() : Map
    }
    class AgencyReloadResult <<model>> {
        +source: String
        +count: int
    }
}

AgencyRegistryScreen --> AgencyRegistryRepository
AgencyRegistryRepository ..> Agency
AgencyRegistryRepository ..> AgencyReloadResult
Agency --> IssueCategory

note as N5
  Penulisan ke tabel agencies dibatasi kebijakan RLS
  agencies_write_super_admin (hanya super admin).
  reloadInferenceServer() memanggil POST /reload-agencies
  agar cache routing server sinkron tanpa restart.
  IssueCategory (9 kelas) dirinci pada diagram model domain.
end note
@enduml
